Program: The Documentary
Title: Girls' Night Out
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p014t2dk
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 18 Feb 2013
Five young women in five cities on a night out with friends. How do men treat women when they are out for a night? The young women compare experiences in Kampala, Ottawa, Rio, Ramallah and Melbourne. (Image: Daniela, from Brazil, and three friends, ready for a night out)